01:30:40.765 --> 01:30:43.200
I ti stvarno vjeruješ
da smo nepotopivi?!


1096
01:30:45.236 --> 01:30:48.506
Moglo bi objasniti kako je
brod preživio svjetski rat


1097
01:30:49.106 --> 01:30:51.676
desetak neuspjelih liftinga lica,

1098
01:30:52.143 --> 01:30:53.511
odmetnički val.

1099
01:30:55.246 --> 01:31:01.052
Da bismo vratili snagu broda,
moramo vratiti gospodina Clarka,


1100
01:31:01.619 --> 01:31:05.056
i ubiti ono
u čemu je god.


1101
01:31:18.436 --> 01:31:19.904
Ako ne uspijemo...

1102
01:31:21.339 --> 01:31:24.241
Vaše pitanje je li
ovaj brod nepotopiv...


1103
01:31:26.911 --> 01:31:29.647
sasvim sigurno će biti odgovoreno.

1104
01:31:35.353 --> 01:31:36.554
O moj Bože!

1105
01:31:37.455 --> 01:31:39.890
Oh, moj jebeni Bože.

1106
01:31:41.892 --> 01:31:44.261
Sranje!

1107
01:31:47.765 --> 01:31:48.632
Lukas?!

1108
01:31:48.666 --> 01:31:49.867
Patrik!

1109
01:31:49.900 --> 01:31:50.735
Vidim ga.

1110
01:31:50.768 --> 01:31:52.603
- Dušo vrati se!
- Čekaj!


1111
01:32:08.586 --> 01:32:09.854
Anne!

1112
01:32:19.430 --> 01:32:22.199
Anne? Jesi li tu?

1113
01:32:32.309 --> 01:32:35.546
Patrick, javi se! Patrik.

1114
01:32:35.579 --> 01:32:36.781
Da, tu sam.

1115
01:32:39.216 --> 01:32:42.119
Pratio sam Lukasa do
dizala, ali njega više nema.


1116
01:32:42.486 --> 01:32:43.754
Gdje si?

1117
01:32:45.790 --> 01:32:48.993
Ne znam, ovaj,
brojevi kabine su E-100s.


1118
01:32:49.093 --> 01:32:50.728
U redu, ostani gdje jesi...

1119
01:34:03.134 --> 01:34:05.202
Očistite put, prolazite!

1120
01:34:05.769 --> 01:34:06.904
Nastavi se kretati, gore.

1121
01:34:06.937 --> 01:34:08.672
I slijedite sigurnosne naredbe.

1122
01:34:13.978 --> 01:34:15.146
Gdje je?

1123
01:34:38.135 --> 01:34:39.303
Dođi!

1124
01:34:45.376 --> 01:34:46.477
Nastavi se kretati!

1125
01:34:46.545 --> 01:34:48.312
S puta! Prolazim!

1126
01:35:17.408 --> 01:35:20.177
Vi niste odavde, zar ne?

1127
01:35:23.648 --> 01:35:26.917
Oprostite, oprostite
na drskosti.


1128
01:35:27.952 --> 01:35:29.554
- Mama?
- Ostani s nama, molim te.


1129
01:35:29.621 --> 01:35:30.622
Lukas?

1130
01:35:30.655 --> 01:35:31.989
Ako želite ostati,

1131
01:35:32.122 --> 01:35:34.091
y-y-ti bi mogao zauzeti moje mjesto!

1132
01:35:34.124 --> 01:35:36.595
Stvarno mi ne smeta!

1133
01:35:36.961 --> 01:35:40.130
Divno je, divno zabavno!

1134
01:35:40.431 --> 01:35:41.999
I mogao sam otići...

1135
01:35:42.733 --> 01:35:44.735
