1140
01:35:51.775 --> 01:35:53.911
- Ništa od ovoga nije stvarno.
- Trebam tvoje tijelo!


1141
01:35:53.944 --> 01:35:55.614
Ali ja te trebam više!

1142
01:35:55.913 --> 01:35:57.682
Zašto bi ti otišao, a ne ja?!

1143
01:35:57.716 --> 01:35:59.850
Jebi me. Ljudi
me čekaju!


1144
01:36:00.017 --> 01:36:02.353
Molim! Preklinjem!

1145
01:36:02.386 --> 01:36:03.487
Lukas!

1146
01:36:03.521 --> 01:36:04.855
Gdje si?!

1147
01:36:06.757 --> 01:36:08.225
Daj mi svoje tijelo!

1148
01:36:10.060 --> 01:36:12.530
Moram sići s ovog broda!

1149
01:36:14.999 --> 01:36:16.267
Stop!

1150
01:36:17.167 --> 01:36:18.802
Gdje si?

1151
01:36:22.973 --> 01:36:25.276
Mislio sam da si otišao kući.

1152
01:36:28.613 --> 01:36:29.714
Je...

1153
