1212
01:41:22.105 --> 01:41:23.373
Gdje si?

1213
01:41:45.095 --> 01:41:47.197
Krećite se i ostanite mirni.

1214
01:41:47.431 --> 01:41:49.299
Sve je to dio predstave!

1215
01:41:51.936 --> 01:41:53.136
Potez!

1216
01:41:54.639 --> 01:41:56.206
Pokret, pokret, pokret!

1217
01:42:02.513 --> 01:42:04.281
Ne puštajte ga s broda!

1218
01:42:08.118 --> 01:42:09.520
Preokrenite vitlo.

1219
01:42:12.023 --> 01:42:15.093
Ne, niže! Spusti ga!

1220
01:42:27.772 --> 01:42:30.908
Mama, zašto ne mogu dalje?

1221
01:42:32.010 --> 01:42:33.611
Oh, Lukas dušo.

1222
01:42:34.112 --> 01:42:36.413
Jackie mi je rekla što se dogodilo.

1223
01:42:37.081 --> 01:42:39.617
Ostavili smo ga u bazenu.

1224
01:42:40.985 --> 01:42:42.720
- Istrunuti...
- s ostalima.


1225
01:42:45.790 --> 01:42:47.290
Tata je govorio...

1226
01:42:49.359 --> 01:42:52.830
