1227
01:42:53.831 --> 01:42:55.533
Kao...

1228
01:42:56.433 --> 01:42:58.503
Kao da pokušavate uloviti ribu...

1229
01:42:59.369 --> 01:43:00.938
golim rukama.

1230
01:43:02.073 --> 01:43:06.343
Koliko god molilo,

1231
01:43:08.813 --> 01:43:10.447
pokušava pobjeći,

1232
01:43:12.950 --> 01:43:14.686
držite se čvrsto.

1233
01:43:20.992 --> 01:43:23.427
I ne bojte se

1234
01:43:24.428 --> 01:43:27.397
da zaprljaš ruke.

1235
01:43:27.665 --> 01:43:32.469
Gdje je ona?

1236
01:43:35.173 --> 01:43:37.809
Čeka mamu.

1237
01:43:41.478 --> 01:43:44.882
Ostani sa mnom zauvijek.

1238
01:43:45.850 --> 01:43:47.719
Opet ćemo biti obitelj.

1239
01:43:49.087 --> 01:43:52.222
Da, ostat ću.

1240
01:44:03.333 --> 01:44:05.570
Beskorisno je pokušavati
otići, Clarky.


1241
01:44:05.603 --> 01:44:08.172
Čak i ako moram plivati,
silazim s ovog broda.


1242
01:44:18.516 --> 01:44:24.055
Vani su zakoni
i prepreke slobodi.


1243
